{"tid":2082024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"珉娥「退出AOA滿1年」首度跟惠晶同框！　粉絲激動：以為再也看不到合體","createTime":"2020-06-27T16:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T19:31:41.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"203fb0dc8c61c44e06e098eb8faf25bb20c9b698","tid":2082024,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"南韓女團AOA前成員珉娥於2019年5月與FNC娛樂合約到期不續約，正式退出團體，後將演藝重心放在演員事業上。她跟惠晶27日在IG曬出與彼此的親密合照，讓不少粉絲相當激動，也有網友驚訝「原來還保持聯絡！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4967/d4967126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4967%2Fd4967126.jpg&h=b96443f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲珉娥2019年約滿退出AOA。（圖／翻攝珉娥IG）<br />\n<br />\n珉娥27日在IG曬出與惠晶聚在一起的照片，兩人將頭靠在一起合照，除了有在室外的照片之外，也有看起來在家裡拍的自拍，展現閨蜜情。而她也在內文寫下了對惠晶的暱稱「申惠咚」（신혜뎡），這是在她退團以來，第一次公開曬出與前隊友的合照，可愛、溫馨的互動吸引了不少網友按讚留言。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4967/d4967130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4967%2Fd4967130.jpg&h=68705e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4967/d4967131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4967%2Fd4967131.jpg&h=a4da5eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4967/d4967129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4967%2Fd4967129.jpg&h=6044515d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲珉娥與惠晶曬出合照。（圖／翻攝珉娥IG）<br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛留言寫下「啊啊啊93line好久不見」、「我真的熱淚盈眶」、「天啊終於同框了」、「還以為看不到合體了，原來還有聯絡」、「好懷念這個組合啊，希望以後常常見面曬照！」。<br />\n<br />\n之前唔係DEL晒IG?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a7548b749db4e7f3d98f385c46bba41cf3d278","tid":2082024,"uid":335530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都靚 做乜走去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be204b314ec096772be3e6378766eca95f75ab1","tid":2082024,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"好細波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d90c24e2d4dc243d458195940310a0e52ba13c","tid":2082024,"uid":345784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"痴線 邊個打邊個 整到認唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42360584d808d995b4f938b0fbbafc8cda9f231b","tid":2082024,"uid":4357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"係鬼第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3bc6312be1e02b9b4e95b1f96c9b9645ce238a","tid":2082024,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c9e3501d5fbf78f781daca4431616533e41bdb","tid":2082024,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"要google個名recall番係咩樣<br />\n再睇番張相<br />\n都係認唔出邊個係"},{"pid":"4b4f796e487d391f695099c2523ca462eb4dc0c0","tid":2082024,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42360584d808d995b4f938b0fbbafc8cda9f231b","tid":2082024,"uid":4357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"係鬼第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"5係咩"},{"pid":"8ffff3d64bf2b5518414df4a87ec900717dadc59","tid":2082024,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T19:31:41.000Z","msg":"第2張相 呀惠晶都打左好多針下<br />\n26歲就打咁多。。。"}]}